rows.label: qst202605_msg0004
rows.name:
You've led us on a merry dance and
no mistake!

rows.label: qst202605_msg0006
rows.name:
Ten'i... When you split off from us...
You did that to protect us, didn't you?

rows.label: qst202605_msg0008
rows.name:
But it looks like you're all right now.
You're not acting weird like before.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0009
rows.name:
Yes, you seem to be
back to your old self.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0010
rows.name: Okay! Shall we move out together?

rows.label: qst202605_msg0012
rows.name: I want you to leave me to my fate.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0013
rows.name:
Are you concerned that you'll
run rampant again?

rows.label: qst202605_msg0015
rows.name:
Hey come on. What happened
before was our fault.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0016
rows.name:
Yeah. We aren't going to let you stew
in your own juices, Ten'i.
